name: Wave 2A — boolean composition
description: ```
A branch condition that composes `and` with an explicit `either … or …`
group lowers to a deterministic `&&` / `||` expression tree on BranchIR.
```
tags: inform7, wave2, codegen

vocab_inline ecom: ```
=== vocabulary ===
An order is a kind of thing.
An order has a total, which is a number.
An order has a status, which is text.
```

source_inline: ```
---
name: screen
parameters: order
vocabulary: ecom.merconfig
---

To screen an order:
  if the order's total is more than 100 and either the order's status is "new" or the order's status is "pending",
    complete with reason "flagged".
```

